snippet.title: Aquatic Supermarket Simulator - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
📢 Coming to Steam in 2024! 
Wishlist 🐟Aquatic Supermarket Simulator now to get free Early Beta Access❗️
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3073580/Aquatic_Supermarket_Simulator/

Run your own aquatic-themed supermarket! Stock shelves with exotic fish🐟 and decorations🖼️, set prices💲, take payments💵, and maintain aquariums🌊. Deliver fish, handle transactions, and ensure your customers are happy.

#aquaticsupermarketgame #supermarketsimulator #pcgaming
